    "description": "<p>At STIE, we adopt a hub-and-spoke model where expertise and skills are centred in one location, and they are used to support project development and implementation throughout the region.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Asia’s rise has been swift, with the region progressing to middle-income status within a single generation, and now accounting for one-third of global trade in goods. In combination with various other factors, these have fuelled growth in Asia’s cities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>There is a huge demand for infrastructure related spending in Asia, driven by urbanisation, shifts in economic power and technological breakthroughs.&nbsp;We are well-positioned to support these regional developments with an approach that is designed to increase the efficient use of resources at our disposal.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
